The paper proposes a technique to improve the generalisation capacity of a deep neural network, which is a common problem in machine learning. The paper focuses on the training of neural networks, which is a core topic in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also mentions the use of the proposed technique in natural language processing (NLP) tasks, which falls under the category of cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper uses the spectral normalization technique, which is a common technique in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
